data.description: Tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac with wide open spaces all around, it is hard to believe you are in a residential golf neighborhood. This one year-old beautiful home was customized by the current owners with upscale features throughout. As you step onto the inviting front porch and then into the foyer you will notice the impressive beamed cathedral ceiling and large windows stretching all across the back wall with views of the spacious back yard and golf course with no other homes in sight.  This open and airy house plan with artfully designed spaces make it a very desirable choice with the tasteful color selections used throughout. The great room with beautiful flooring, high ceilings, cozy gas fireplace all open to the kitchen area with a sit up breakfast bar, built in countertop 5 burner gas range, wall oven and microwave, lighted accent cabinets, and farm sink.  The bright and light dining area looks out over the patio and backyard. The deluxe primary suite has a jacuzzi tub, walk-in tiled shower, double sinks and an enormous closet which adjoins the utility room. Next to the walk through garage  door is the handy mudroom that helps keep things organized. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath occupy the opposite side of the home and the forth bedroom near the front makes an equally useful study with uniquely designed barn door. The home is 2327 SF per the appraiser measurement.   The exterior features of the home are: Sprinkler System, Impact Resistant Roof, Guttering, 3 Car Garage and there is a Tankless Hot Water Heater as well for endless hot water.  The current owners have added many upgrades inside and out: Premium wrought iron fencing - Extended concrete on patio and added concrete sidewalks to side of house - French Drains - River Rock pathways - Perennial garden beds with drip irrigation and many upgrades to the interior. A complete list is available.   Enjoy entertaining family and friends on the oversized back patio while enjoying the beautiful Oklahoma Sunsets . If you are still wondering what elevates the desirability of this property, pick up the phone and call for your own personal private showing.
